cenary Sub-Zero, Hanzo Hasashi is exiled to the torturous Netherrealm. There, in exchange for his servitude to the sinister Quan Chi, he’s given a chance to avenge his family – and is resurrected as Scorpion, a lost soul bent on revenge. Back on Earthrealm, Lord Raiden gathers a team of elite warriors – Shaolin monk Liu Kang, Special Forces officer Sonya Blade and action star Johnny Cage – an unlikely band of heroes with one chance to save humanity. To do this, they must defeat Shang Tsung’s horde of Outworld gladiators and reign over the Mortal Kombat tournament.","genre_ids":[16,28,14],"popularity":2.9504,"vote_count":1435,"poster_path":"/iBvo3qOPcmhlqAaJcXcQHtx2qLk.jpg","release_date":"2020-04-12","vote_average":8.09,"backdrop_path":"/vw3zNfzvnVNF7nIjpiEgcdznfeC.jpg","original_title":"Mortal Kombat Legends: Scorpion's Revenge","original_language":"en"},{"id":12444,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1","video":false,"overview":"Harry, Ron and Hermione walk away from their last year at Hogwarts to find and destroy the remaining Horcruxes, putting an end to Voldemort's bid for immortality. But with Harry's beloved Dumbledore dead and Voldemort's unscrupulous Death Eaters on the loose, the world is more dangerous than ever.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":14.4953,"vote_count":20111,"poster_path":"/iGoXIpQb7Pot00EEdwpwPajheZ5.jpg","release_date":"2010-11-17","vote_average":7.736,"backdrop_path":"/AqLcLsGGTzAjm3pCCq0CZCQrp6m.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1","original_language":"en"},{"id":12445,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2","video":false,"overview":"Harry, Ron and Hermione continue their quest to vanquish the evil Voldemort once and for all. Just as things begin to look hopeless for the young wizards, Harry discovers a trio of magical objects that endow him with powers to rival Voldemort's formidable skills.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":15.5433,"vote_count":21694,"poster_path":"/c54HpQmuwXjHq2C9wmoACjxoom3.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-12","vote_average":8.08,"backdrop_path":"/cbcpDn6XJaIGoOil1bKuskU8ds4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":12448,"adult":false,"title":"The Hunchback of Notre Dame II","video":false,"overview":"Now that Frollo is gone, Quasimodo rings the bell with the help of his new friend and Esmeralda's and Phoebus' little son, Zephyr. But when Quasi stops by a traveling circus owned by evil magician Sarousch, he falls for Madellaine, Sarouch's assistant.","genre_ids":[16,10751,35,10749],"popularity":2.6644,"vote_count":843,"poster_path":"/14PSM6n9VSsiUwJhT0WZbgOuNvP.jpg","release_date":"2002-02-06","vote_average":5.378,"backdrop_path":"/bVgzCYEQ6HaWnA6XW3uqit5vxeF.jpg","original_title":"The Hunchback of Notre Dame II","original_language":"en"},{"id":472516,"adult":false,"title":"The Moment You Fall in Love","video":false,"overview":"Following Natsuki Enomoto's confession rehearsals with Yuu Setoguchi, their younger siblings Kotarou and Hina struggle to confess their own love. Despite a disastrous first meeting in middle school with her upperclassman Koyuki Ayase, Hina’s heart is captured by his warm smile. Initially confused by these newfound feelings, Hina soon realizes that she has fallen in love for the very first time.  Chasing after her brother Yuu and her crush Koyuki, Hina also enrolls in Sakuragaoka High School; but the threads of love are far-reaching, and they entangle Hina and her friends. Boisterous but sensitive, Hina hopes to confess her feelings to the tender-hearted Koyuki. Meanwhile, Kotarou, oblivious to his own feelings for her, is determined to always keep Hina smiling.  This movie follows Hina, Kotarou, and Koyuki in high school. Their youthful love forges new relationships, but also threatens to break others.","genre_ids":[18,16,10749,35],"popularity":1.0959,"vote_count":137,"poster_path":"/b3NQEmgAYKTDuAXSE0f294lrE4Q.jpg","release_date":"2016-12-17","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/lTbYegQ35QRWlWvDqYwS0okFiY4.jpg","original_title":"好きになるその瞬間を。～告白実行委員会～","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12242,"adult":false,"title":"Mulan II","video":false,"overview":"Fa Mulan gets the surprise of her young life when her love, Captain Li Shang asks for her hand in marriage. Before the two can have their happily ever after, the Emperor assigns them a secret mission, to escort three princesses to Chang'an, China. Mushu is determined to drive a wedge between the couple after he learns that he will lose his guardian job if Mulan marries into the Li family.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,28],"popularity":3.3291,"vote_count":2474,"poster_path":"/mIHE3BKyAKG8ocRAoZuCQN1NTv9.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-03","vote_average":6.513,"backdrop_path":"/2Zv86BI4QqztR19fwFErXyr59h.jpg","original_title":"Mulan II","original_language":"en"},{"id":12593,"adult":false,"title":"Fritz the Cat","video":false,"overview":"In late 1960s New York City, fed up with monotonous college life and police repression, free-spirited Fritz, an impenitent seducer and unrestrained party-animal, decides to explore the world. And just like that, as he flees NYC, heading to San Francisco, Fritz embarks on an endless adventure of illumination. Immersed in a world surrounded by drugs and sex, Fritz participates in mad orgies, brings about a revolution, incites mass urban riots, and crosses paths with drug-addled Nazi bikers.","genre_ids":[16,35,18],"popularity":1.089,"vote_count":374,"poster_path":"/llgCW1Y99WO7DNiX3ZOncLJBIAm.jpg","release_date":"1972-04-14","vote_average":6.187,"backdrop_path":"/udY0Gw8BB99jsJzARsJhctLqUZ6.jpg","original_title":"Fritz the Cat","original_language":"en"},{"id":12594,"adult":false,"title":"Wishmaster 2: Evil Never Dies","video":false,"overview":"During a failed art heist, the Djinn is once again liberated. This time, to complete the 1001 wishes that he needs before the final 3, he lets himself go to prison, where he starts his evil reign twisting the hopes of the prisoners. Meanwhile, the woman who set him free accidentally, Morgana, tries to find a way to stop him, aided by a young priest.","genre_ids":[14,27],"popularity":2.1767,"vote_count":314,"poster_path":"/g3FXNYaCDFoQILCbYqFdv6V01ep.jpg","release_date":"1999-03-12","vote_average":5.672,"backdrop_path":"/kJJxRr7OHo6UPNXZI89DoIu6Eov.jpg","original_title":"Wishmaster 2: Evil Never Dies","original_language":"en"},{"id":12600,"adult":false,"title":"Pokémon 4Ever","video":false,"overview":"In order to escape a greedy Pokémon hunter, Celebi must use the last of its energy to travel through time to the present day. Celebi brings along Sammy, a boy who had been trying to protect it. Along with Ash, Pikachu, and the rest of the gang, Sammy and Celebi must encounter an enemy far more advanced than the hunter, with the fate of the forest hanging in the balance.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,878,10751],"popularity":2.7387,"vote_count":449,"poster_path":"/thz83PS9twtVBEEAM59J1bh75nU.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-06","vote_average":6.468,"backdrop_path":"/lnwNzJdU4gMlgoQlaT8HgSI2OpD.jpg","original_title":"劇場版ポケットモンスター セレビィ 時を超えた遭遇","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt37284198","twitter_id":"heicat_movie_jp","facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q135420006","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":"heicat_movie_jp","facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":107346,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"CA","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-05T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-07-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descript